title: Debate, Rep. Conor Lamb, Rep, Tim Ryan
itunes:title: Debate, Rep. Conor Lamb, Rep, Tim Ryan
description:
Guests: Rep. Tim Ryan, a Democrat representing Ohio's 13th congressional district, Clark Kendall, President and CEO Kendall Capital, Rep. Conor Lamb, a Democrat representing Pennsylvania's 17th congressional district, Matt Gorman, Vice President at Targeted Victory & Former NRCC Communications, Brandon Neal, Democratic strategist, and former senior advisor to Pete Buttigieg’s Presidential Campaign, and Kimberly Guilfoyle, Trump campaign senior advisor and National Chair of the 2020 Trump Victory Finance Committee.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
